{
  "title":       "Panels",
  "url":         "/blog/panels/",
  "permalink":   "http://localhost:1313/blog/panels/",
  "date":        "2025-02-10",
  "tags":        ["panels","layout"],
  "summary":     "Every titled container in the theme is one parametric partial.",
  "readingTime": 2,
  "content":     "\u003cp\u003eEvery titled container on this site is \u003ccode\u003epartials/panel.html\u003c/code\u003e called with\na different \u003ccode\u003evariant\u003c/code\u003e. Pass a dict with \u003ccode\u003etitle\u003c/code\u003e, \u003ccode\u003enumber\u003c/code\u003e, \u003ccode\u003evariant\u003c/code\u003e,\nand content:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"chroma\"\u003e\u003ccode class=\"language-go-html-template\" data-lang=\"go-html-template\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cp\"\u003e{{\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003epartial\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;panel.html\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nx\"\u003edict\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e  \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e   \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;Posts\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e  \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;variant\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;list\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e  \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026#34;items\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e   \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003e.Pages\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"w\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cp\"\u003e}}\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"plain\"\u003ePlain\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFreeform HTML in a titled border. Hover to see the border and header\nhighlight together.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel__header\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__title\"\u003eAbout\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eA titled container with freeform HTML content. The title sits on the top border.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"list--preview\"\u003eList + Preview\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA list panel paired with a preview panel. Clicking an item in the list\nswaps the preview content without a page navigation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"grid-list-preview\" style=\"margin:1rem 0;\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"panel panel--list\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"region\" data-count=\"1 of 3\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"panel__header\"\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"panel__number\"\u003e[1]\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__separator\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"panel__title\"\u003eItems\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\n        \u003cul class=\"panel__list\"\u003e\n          \u003cli class=\"panel__list-item\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"panel__list-link js-demo-preview-link panel__list-link--active\" data-preview-url=\"#demo-preview-1\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__list-title\"\u003eFirst item\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__list-meta\"\u003eMarch 1, 2025\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli class=\"panel__list-item\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"panel__list-link js-demo-preview-link\" data-preview-url=\"#demo-preview-2\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__list-title\"\u003eSecond item\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__list-meta\"\u003eFebruary 14, 2025\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n          \u003cli class=\"panel__list-item\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"panel__list-link js-demo-preview-link\" data-preview-url=\"#demo-preview-3\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__list-title\"\u003eThird item\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__list-meta\"\u003eJanuary 5, 2025\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"js-scroll-indicator\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"panel panel--preview\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"region\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"panel__header\"\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"panel__number\"\u003e[2]\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__separator\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"panel__title js-demo-preview-title\"\u003eFirst item\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"panel__content js-demo-preview-content\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv id=\"demo-preview-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis is the preview for the first item. Click a different entry in the list panel to swap the content here.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOn real list pages (like the blog index), \u003ccode\u003elist-preview.js\u003c/code\u003e fetches \u003ccode\u003eindex.json\u003c/code\u003e once and swaps from memory. This demo uses inline content instead.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv id=\"demo-preview-2\" style=\"display:none\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSecond item selected. The preview title updates and the list panel counter tracks which item is active.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe scroll indicator on the right edge of each panel updates as content changes height.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv id=\"demo-preview-3\" style=\"display:none\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThird item. On pages without JavaScript the list items are plain links that navigate to the full page \u0026mdash; the preview is a progressive enhancement.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"js-scroll-indicator\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cscript type=\"module\"\u003e\n  {\n    const links = document.querySelectorAll('.js-demo-preview-link');\n    const title = document.querySelector('.js-demo-preview-title');\n    const content = document.querySelector('.js-demo-preview-content');\n    const listPanel = links[0]?.closest('.panel--list');\n    links.forEach((link, i) =\u003e {\n      link.addEventListener('click', (e) =\u003e {\n        e.preventDefault();\n        links.forEach(l =\u003e l.classList.remove('panel__list-link--active'));\n        link.classList.add('panel__list-link--active');\n        if (listPanel) listPanel.setAttribute('data-count', `${i+1} of ${links.length}`);\n        if (title) title.textContent = link.querySelector('.panel__list-title').textContent;\n        content.querySelectorAll(':scope \u003e div').forEach(d =\u003e d.style.display = 'none');\n        const target = document.querySelector(link.dataset.previewUrl);\n        if (target) target.style.display = '';\n      });\n    });\n  }\n  \u003c/script\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOn real section pages (like the blog index) \u003ccode\u003elist-preview.js\u003c/code\u003e fetches\n\u003ccode\u003eindex.json\u003c/code\u003e once and renders from memory. Without JavaScript the list\nitems are plain links to the full pages.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"tabs\"\u003eTabs\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDual-mode: tab switchers in the border when narrow, side-by-side\ncolumns when wide. Resize the window to see both states.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"panel panel--tab js-check-width\"\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel__header\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__title\"\u003eTabs\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__separator\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"panel__tabs\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__tab panel__tab--active\"\n                  data-tab-id=\"tab-0\"\n                  data-tab-num=\"1\"\n                  data-tab-title=\"Narrow\"\u003eNarrow\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__tab-separator\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__tab\"\n                  data-tab-id=\"tab-1\"\n                  data-tab-num=\"2\"\n                  data-tab-title=\"Wider\"\u003eWider\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__tab-separator\"\u003e-\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__tab\"\n                  data-tab-id=\"tab-2\"\n                  data-tab-num=\"3\"\n                  data-tab-title=\"Keyboard\"\u003eKeyboard\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__note\"\u003e(resize window)\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__tab-contents\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"tab-0\" class=\"panel__tab-content panel__tab-content--active\" data-tab-title=\"Narrow\"\u003e\n          \u003cp\u003eBelow the width threshold, tab names in the border act as switchers.\u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"tab-1\" class=\"panel__tab-content\" data-tab-title=\"Wider\"\u003e\n          \u003cp\u003eOnce wide enough, all tabs render side-by-side as columns.\u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"tab-2\" class=\"panel__tab-content\" data-tab-title=\"Keyboard\"\u003e\n          \u003cp\u003eFocus a tab and use \u003ckbd\u003eArrowLeft\u003c/kbd\u003e/\u003ckbd\u003eArrowRight\u003c/kbd\u003e to navigate.\u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"input\"\u003eInput\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA prompt-style wrapper. The border and title switch to \u003ccode\u003e--base0C\u003c/code\u003e on\nfocus and the textarea auto-grows as you type.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"panel panel--input\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"panel__header\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__title\"\u003eScript\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__note\"\u003e(auto-grows)\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\n      \u003ctextarea placeholder=\"type here…\" spellcheck=\"false\"\u003e#!/bin/bash\necho \"Textareas auto-grow as you type.\"\u003c/textarea\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n"
},
{
  "title":       "Layouts",
  "url":         "/blog/layouts/",
  "permalink":   "http://localhost:1313/blog/layouts/",
  "date":        "2025-01-22",
  "tags":        ["layout","grid"],
  "summary":     "Page skeleton and a small family of responsive grid classes.",
  "readingTime": 1,
  "content":     "\u003cp\u003eEvery page is \u003ccode\u003enav\u003c/code\u003e + \u003ccode\u003emain\u003c/code\u003e + \u003ccode\u003efooter\u003c/code\u003e inside a centred \u003ccode\u003e.container\u003c/code\u003e\n(max 1500px). \u003ccode\u003emain\u003c/code\u003e holds either a single panel or a grid of panels.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"grid-classes\"\u003eGrid classes\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAll grids collapse to a single column at 768px.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"grid-2col\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003e.grid-2col\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"grid-2col\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eLeft column.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eRight column.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"grid-3col\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003e.grid-3col\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCollapses to two columns at 992px, then one at 768px.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"grid-3col\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eOne\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eTwo\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThree\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"grid-main-sidebar\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003e.grid-main-sidebar\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"grid-main-sidebar\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__header\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__title\"\u003eSidebar\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e1fr.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__header\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__title\"\u003eMain\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e2fr.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"grid-auto-fit\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003e.grid-auto-fit\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs many 300px-min columns as the container allows.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"grid-auto-fit\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eCard\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eCard\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eCard\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eCard\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"grid-master-stack\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003e.grid-master-stack\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"grid-master-stack\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__header\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__title\"\u003eMaster\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e2fr.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"stack\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eStack 1\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eStack 2\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eStack 3\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"grid-monocle\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003e.grid-monocle\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"grid-monocle\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__header\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"panel__title\"\u003eFull-width\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSingle-column grid with consistent gap.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"panel\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"panel__content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSecond panel.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"special-case-grids\"\u003eSpecial-case grids\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003e.grid-list-preview\u003c/code\u003e — blog and taxonomy lists. Scrollable\ntitle list (300px min) + preview pane (2fr).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003e.home-grid\u003c/code\u003e — homepage. 2fr intro + 1fr recent posts.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n"
},
{
  "title":       "Nav",
  "url":         "/blog/nav/",
  "permalink":   "http://localhost:1313/blog/nav/",
  "date":        "2025-01-19",
  "tags":        ["nav","layout","responsive"],
  "summary":     "Chevron-clipped bar with a title tab and link pills.",
  "readingTime": 1,
  "content":     "\u003cp\u003eA flex row of \u003ccode\u003eclip-path\u003c/code\u003e chevron shapes. Title tab on the left, menu\npills on the right. No JavaScript.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"plain\"\u003ePlain\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cnav class=\"site-nav\" aria-label=\"Plain nav demo\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0;\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"site-nav__inner\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"site-nav__title\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"site-nav__title-text\"\u003eTitle\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003cul class=\"site-nav__menu\"\u003e\n      \u003cli class=\"site-nav__item\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"site-nav__link\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"site-nav__link-text\"\u003eHome\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli class=\"site-nav__item\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"site-nav__link\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"site-nav__link-text\"\u003eBlog\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli class=\"site-nav__item\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"site-nav__link\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"site-nav__link-text\"\u003eAbout\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/nav\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"with-icons\"\u003eWith icons\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTitle icon from \u003ccode\u003esite.Params.titleIcon\u003c/code\u003e; link icons from each menu\nentry\u0026rsquo;s \u003ccode\u003eparams.icon\u003c/code\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cnav class=\"site-nav\" aria-label=\"Icon nav demo\" style=\"margin: 1rem 0;\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"site-nav__inner\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"site-nav__title\"\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"icon site-nav__icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u0026#xf120;\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"site-nav__title-text\"\u003etui\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003cul class=\"site-nav__menu\"\u003e\n      \u003cli class=\"site-nav__item\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"#\" class=\"site-nav__link\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"icon site-